{"tid":1705941,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"1400 緊急民間記者會","createTime":"2019-11-11T03:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:48:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"75a36b71513e1c2abedb815cb9ced893219192a2","tid":1705941,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:23:25.000Z","msg":"各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n<br />\n緊急採訪通知<br />\n<br />\n因應昨天晚上「八區開花」及今天早上「黎明行動」而出現的各區警暴情況，民間記者會將作出有關回應。現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年11月11日（星期一)<br />\n時間：下午2 時<br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，如有查詢可向金先生查詢。<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2019年11月11日<br />\n<br />\nDear members of the press,<br />\n<br />\nRe: Invitation to an Emergency Press Conference<br />\n <br />\nThe Citizens&rsquo; Press Conference will be holding an emergency press conference to give response to the serial events of anti-human behaviour by the police with regards to the protests on the streets from yesterday evening onwards overnight and in the morning today.<br />\n<br />\nWe hereby cordially invite your organisation to attend our press conference. The details of the event are as follows:<br />\n  <br />\nDate: 11 Nov 2019<br />\nTime: 2:00 PM<br />\n<br />\nEmail: kim@citizenspc.org<br />\n <br />\nShould you have any further questions, please do not hesitate to contact our representative with the information as stated above.  Thank you for your kind attention.<br />\n <br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\nCitizens&rsquo; Press Conference"},{"pid":"6b4f0afd33303c8868d8980715d4b9df410d8630","tid":1705941,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf534f12f0e124a2d7958fb9442155d3de5a1c6","tid":1705941,"uid":4355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41dc302daadcb2d9f639db01d314342a80cc5a9b","tid":1705941,"uid":13844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:24:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4267478ae1493eace186b3f66a5bcfce445e5e6b","tid":1705941,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32416ce8894731c9f11b8830af4ecc56e28b50f9","tid":1705941,"uid":197243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db04f975c6ae4d8dae4b44a0391d2d25b13eda0","tid":1705941,"uid":128287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:26:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8146b78e32538996173a4a28ec5c807da2a20da5","tid":1705941,"uid":211300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45e27443fa7fd511010ace302021698901b5de77","tid":1705941,"uid":163124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51a0399f2ca8571723747f975b062d7efc97b79","tid":1705941,"uid":240362